<notes>
The vehicle's armament fluff classifies the individual Sniper weapon as a cannon. However, it is not a true Sniper Artillery Cannon, which is lighter and shorter ranged than a regular Sniper Artillery Piece. The Ballista's record sheet and weapon break down shows that the Sniper Artillery weapon is in fact listed as an Artillery Piece.
</notes>

